{"tid":2021182,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家要準備情緒再進入低谷","createTime":"2020-05-17T14:32:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T10:36:10.000Z","uid":325346,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"828d6c6ce45380fa8cfacea132f3030151f2a7e5","tid":2021182,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T14:32:12.000Z","msg":"經歷了接近一年的社會抗爭<br />\n當中有些人失去了愛情、親情、友情<br />\n當中牽涉到信任與與人相處的問題<br />\n在連登俾人話五毛、俾連衛兵搞係好小事、可以唔計較<br />\n但面對真實的關係與傷害係另一回事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上星期五一天發生左咁多事<br />\n情緒又進入左低潮<br />\n覺得自己好無用、改變唔到件事、又無勇氣出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家大家明知場仗要點打<br />\n但因為有負擔而卻步（家庭、未來、生活的困難）<br />\n本來有些人的家庭關係在疫症這幾個月修復了表面的部份、但未來又可能再惡劣起來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家要有思想準備、低處未算低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係放負、大家要善待自己先有能力對人好、做人盡左力盡左自己責任就得。<br />\n<br />\n連衛兵咪撚再搞我、係乜立場睇我的帖就知、唔洗解釋咁多。"},{"pid":"e4934601444dd4cd123fda79eef522f23cecae57","tid":2021182,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T14:33:34.000Z","msg":"係 基本上527惡歌法過硬咁滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6d3d46d3b3f55fd7162a5a35cc00efadb74514","tid":2021182,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e4934601444dd4cd123fda79eef522f23cecae57","tid":2021182,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T14:33:34.000Z","msg":"係 基本上527惡歌法過硬咁滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T14:36:39.000Z","msg":"覺得出唔出去都好矛盾<br />\n心裡覺得要出去<br />\n但出去就預左俾狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁可以點？而家立埋23條都仲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4b447c60155412cd9899359ef21ac2130712ea","tid":2021182,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T14:40:48.000Z","msg":"無論點大家都要團結<br />\n互相關心<br />\n唔好一黎就屌"},{"pid":"aad6c5b60696bb5ad6214897cd1237c13ee877ff","tid":2021182,"uid":80762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:37:32.000Z","msg":"低緊了"},{"pid":"b23276b87d8dad7f43c245310cee6569f476cf71","tid":2021182,"uid":271303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:41:13.000Z","msg":"有能力就好移民"},{"pid":"fbb2a1ae054fae0a891181bba02cbc07842cd0df","tid":2021182,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b23276b87d8dad7f43c245310cee6569f476cf71","tid":2021182,"uid":271303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:41:13.000Z","msg":"有能力就好移民"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:50:30.000Z","msg":"無能力<br />\nBurn with HK"},{"pid":"695c959394a80b04078f42504d2d78f24a53f5ec","tid":2021182,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aad6c5b60696bb5ad6214897cd1237c13ee877ff","tid":2021182,"uid":80762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:37:32.000Z","msg":"低緊了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:51:10.000Z","msg":"低谷更要讓自己開心"},{"pid":"cc2f2a18920b09b02816129a2cf23469d60117d1","tid":2021182,"uid":80762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"695c959394a80b04078f42504d2d78f24a53f5ec","tid":2021182,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aad6c5b60696bb5ad6214897cd1237c13ee877ff","tid":2021182,"uid":80762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:37:32.000Z","msg":"低緊了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:51:10.000Z","msg":"低谷更要讓自己開心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:54:47.000Z","msg":"開不了心 身邊啲人個個灰曬心，我其實未至於灰心，但我好無力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d51917d71b7d5ecad6ce5786f6b4d747259ba8b","tid":2021182,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc2f2a18920b09b02816129a2cf23469d60117d1","t